{
  "stem": "18186.2",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "So we went to the Jewish cemetery.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And when we got there, the same thing was there happening.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "Everybody was-- there's crying and shooting was going on.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "So we decided not to go into the cemetery, and go-- we were going into further into the fields, to the farm-- where the farmers lived.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And finally it started-- we find-- there at that time, they were cut-- they were-- that was the time when they were cutting the corn and the wheat, and they put such-- they made such a things heaped, you know, for this to dry.",
      "word_count": 44
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And we went into this.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And each one was like separately.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And we-- and then we went into a barn.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And then some-- during the night, I hear people walking and yelling, Ukrainian, the police.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "We police, if there's anybody there, out.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "Otherwise, we'll kill you.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "So we just-- we-- the three of us, we-- we were crawling on our stomach out from the barn.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And we went further into the-- again, into the fields.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And for some reason we were lucky, they didn't see us.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "They didn't hear anything.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "And then day came, daytime came.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "And we got up, out of [INAUDIBLE], and we started to walk to look for a place where there's no Ukrainian people, where the Polish people live.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "And this-- and then they met two more, two other kids, boys, who-- who-- and we teamed up.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "And we all were walking together, just walking in the middle of the streets, didn't know who-- the people didn't know us.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "The kids didn't know us.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "They didn't say-- we just walked.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And then-- and then we-- until we reached the Polish, Wirke, that town.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, yeah.",
      "word_count": 2
    }
  ],
